   "body" : "My favorite configuration for gitian building is Linux Mint 19.1 (based on Ubuntu 18.04) with LXC 3.0.3.\r\n\r\nFaced disk space issues. This `gitian-builder` patch works well:\r\n```\r\ndiff --git a/bin/make-base-vm b/bin/make-base-vm\r\nindex 916c11f..152f8bc 100755\r\n--- a/bin/make-base-vm\r\n+++ b/bin/make-base-vm\r\n@@ -264,7 +264,7 @@ if [ $LXC = \"1\" ]; then\r\n       fi\r\n     fi\r\n   fi\r\n-  dd if=/dev/zero of=$OUT-lxc bs=1M count=1 seek=10240\r\n+  dd if=/dev/zero of=$OUT-lxc bs=1M count=1 seek=15360\r\n   /sbin/mkfs.ext4 -F $OUT-lxc\r\n   t=`mktemp -d gitian.XXXXXXXX`\r\n   sudo mount $OUT-lxc $t\r\n```\r\n\r\nRefs:\r\n- https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/15541#issuecomment-470160960 and https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/15549#issuecomment-470330012 by @laanwj \r\n- https://github.com/devrandom/gitian-builder/pull/172 by @luke-jr ",
